{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji15","name":"毛泽东全集第15卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji15.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致萧克电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致萧克电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年11月24日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目前时局在转变关头，我党一面须坚持各抗日根据地，一面须准备对付蒋介石的“剿共”战争。平西、平北及冀东区域的坚持与发展，增加了对整个局势的意义，望从艰难中支持下去，与聂、彭打成一片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军委历来对你处没有多少帮助，今后将更少帮助，一切望你及同志们独立支持之。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1940,"month":11,"day":24}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":242,"page_end":242},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}